**a)** Create a line graph that gives the daily maximum temperature for 2005. *Make sure the x-axis is a date and covers the whole year.*
```{r}
FlagMaxTemp2005<-FlagMaxTemp%>%
  filter(Year==2005)
```

```{r}
FlagMaxTemp20052<-FlagMaxTemp2005%>%
  select(-X)%>%
  pivot_longer(cols=starts_with("X"),names_to="Day",values_to="MaxTemp")%>%
  mutate(Day = as.integer(str_remove_all(as.character(Day),"X")))%>%
  mutate(Date=make_date(Year,Month,Day))%>%
